      <title>印度影子银行 Shriram 为该行业寻求创纪录的离岸贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/indian-shadow-bank-shriram-seeks-record-offshore-loan-for-sector</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Shriram Finance Ltd. 正就一笔约 12.5 亿美元的社会贷款进行深入谈判，这笔交易将成为印度影子银行有史以来最大的离岸贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/indian-shadow-bank-shriram-seeks-record-offshore-loan-for-sector</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 01:17:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝恩资本将向 KKR 发起 42 亿美元敌意收购富士软件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/bain-to-make-4-2-billion-hostile-bid-for-fuji-soft-against-kkr</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝恩资本计划在未获得日本软件公司富士软件董事会支持的情况下竞购该公司股票，由此在日本对 KKR &amp; Co. 发起罕见的敌意收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/bain-to-make-4-2-billion-hostile-bid-for-fuji-soft-against-kkr</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 00:47:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本田与日产的潜在合并能带来什么好处？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/what-would-honda-gain-from-potential-merger-with-nissan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦格理资本亚洲汽车业务主管 James Hong 分享了他对本田汽车公司和日产汽车公司潜在合并的看法。据知情人士透露，这两家日本汽车制造商一直在就合并进行初步谈判。Hong 在“彭博：亚洲交易”节目中发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/what-would-honda-gain-from-potential-merger-with-nissan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 00:47:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金下跌，因市场关注美联储明年利率前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/gold-xauusd-holds-before-expected-us-rate-cut-as-traders-weigh-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储即将公布利率决定，黄金价格在之前保持下跌，交易员们正在关注明年货币政策路径的线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/gold-xauusd-holds-before-expected-us-rate-cut-as-traders-weigh-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 00:38:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币涨势在首次突破 108,000 美元后暂停</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/bitcoin-btc-rally-pauses-after-scaling-108-000-for-the-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员等待美联储预期中的降息，并评估当选总统唐纳德·特朗普对加密货币的支持带来的乐观情绪，比特币在首次突破 108,000 美元后稍作喘息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/bitcoin-btc-rally-pauses-after-scaling-108-000-for-the-first-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 00:38:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
