      <title>香港监管机构在上市调查中搜查金融公司办公室</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/hong-kong-said-to-probe-local-financiers-over-nasdaq-listings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，香港证券监管机构上个月搜查了大约十几家金融公司和个人的办公室，作为对纳斯达克交易所上市公司调查的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/hong-kong-said-to-probe-local-financiers-over-nasdaq-listings</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 00:30:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
